You can add a Customer Insights dashboard to a page.

Required editions and user permissions:
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition. Requires a CRM Analytics Growth or CRM Analytics Plus license.

Permission sets needed:
To create and manage the app: Manage CRM Analytics Templated Apps
To use CRM Analytics template apps: Use CRM Analytics Templated Apps

Embed the Accounts Dashboard
On the Accounts tab, click the Setup icon, and select Edit Page.
From the Components menu on the left, select the CRM Analytics dashboard and drag it onto your dashboard.
Select the Accounts Embedded dashboard.

Embed the Case Dashboard
On the Cases tab, click the Setup icon, and select Edit Page.
From the Components menu on the left, select the CRM Analytics dashboard and drag it onto your dashboard.
Select the Case Embedded dashboard.

Embed the Opportunity Dashboard
On the Opportunities tab, click the Setup icon, and select Edit Page.
From the Components menu on the left, select the CRM Analytics dashboard and drag it onto your dashboard.
Select the Opportunity Embedded dashboard.
title: Embedding Customer Insights Dashboards in Salesforce
